{"lemma":"نُكْتَةٌ","slug":"نُكْتَةٌ","root":"ن.ك.ت","root_slug":"ن-ك-ت","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ك-ت","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n40466"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8F%D9%83%D9%92%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"point, dot, tittle, spot"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"joke, anecdote, witticism"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"conceit (artificial equivocal answer)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"odd person"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"merry-andrew, clown, buffoon"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n40466","headword_ar":"نُكَتَةٌ","root":"nkt","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A point; a dot; a speck; a minute spot; i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqoTapN","text_ar":"نُقْطَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukatN","text_ar":"نُكَتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, &c) agreeably with analogy, (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nikaAtN","text_ar":"نِكَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) deviating from analogy, and, accord. to some,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukaAtN","text_ar":"نُكَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to be added"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liloA_i$obaAEi","text_ar":"لِلْاـِشْبَاعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or to render the sound of the fet-hah full, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruxaAlN","text_ar":"رُخَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) the last of these pls. has been heard [from the classical Arabs]; (Esh-Shiháb, in the Expos. of the Shifà;) or it is vulgar. (Msb.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukotapN","text_ar":"نُكْتَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small spot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling dirt upon a mirror:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukotapN sawodaA'u","text_ar":"نُكْتَةٌ سَوْدَاءُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"black"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mark, like a spot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dot, resembling dirt upon a mirror"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sword"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, from a trad.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukotapN","text_ar":"نُكْتَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A spot in the eye;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what resembles a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqorap","text_ar":"وَقْرَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the eye."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b4-  [↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakotN","text_ar":"نَكْتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"seems to be a quasi-pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukotapN","text_ar":"نُكْتَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqoTN","text_ar":"نَقْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to be (by some persons in the present day) of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqoTapN","text_ar":"نُقْطَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Any small spots,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"specks, in a thing, differing therefrom in colour."},{"kind":"text","text":"Such I suppose to be meant by the words in the L,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kl~ naqoTK fY $Y' xAlf lwnh nakotN","text_ar":"كلّ نَقْطٍ فى شىء خالف لونه نَكْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukotapN","text_ar":"نُكْتَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A nice, subtile, subtilely excogitated, quaint,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2847},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"facetious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"witty, saying, expression,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"allusion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laTiyfap","text_ar":"لَطِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that makes an impression upon the heart;"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~akotu","text_ar":"النَّكْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the striking the ground with a stick &c., so as to make a mark, or marks, upon it with its extremity]: also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a question educed by reflection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlt~afak~uri","text_ar":"بِالتَّفَكُّرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as the passage here translated is given in the Kull, p. 362, but in the TA"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAlnql","text_ar":"بالنقل"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is an evident mistake, as might be shown by many authorities,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which makes an impression upon the heart, on hearing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"considering which one generally makes marks upon the ground with the finger"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Fenáree's Expos. of the Telweeh:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a nice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"subtile, saying, expression,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"allusion, that requires one to reflect, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"induces one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to make marks upon the ground with a stick"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(from a scholium quoted by De Sacy, Anthol. Gr. Ar., 303:) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a nice, subtile, abstruse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mystical, point,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"allusion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"point of a saying"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sentence, especially one that is difficult to be understood: a conceit expressed in words difficult to be understood: a quaint conceit: a point of wit: a facetious saying"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"allusion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl., generally,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukatN","text_ar":"نُكَتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA'a binukotahK","text_ar":"جَاءَ بِنُكْتَهٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He uttered a nice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"subtile, saying, expression,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"allusion, &c."},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D9%86%D9%83%D8%AA%D8%A9/","headword_ar":"نكتة","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23812#9e3177","body_html":"<span>النكتة: هي مسألة لطيفة أخرجت بدقة نظر وإمعان، من: نكت رمحه بأرض، إذا أثر فيها وسميت المسألة الدقيقة: نكتة؛ لتأثير الخواطر في استنباطها.</span>"}]}}